NAME
    Perl::Editor::Plugin::Squish - Perl Editor plugin for Perl::Squish

DESCRIPTION
    This is a simple plugin for the Perl Refactoring Editor API that
    provides the ability to "Squish" the current document as described in
    the perl.com article:

    <http://www.perl.com/pub/a/2005/06/09/ppi.html>

SUPPORT
    Bugs should always be submitted via the CPAN bug tracker, located at

    <http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/ReportBug.html?Queue=Perl-Editor-Plugin-Squis
    h>

    For general comments, contact the author.

